{
  "stem": "979.5",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this is some story, eh?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Quite a busy life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now everything's like normal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So because, because all we had before-- some story-- like, when you start thinking of it, how did you make all this?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, how do you make out?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we were sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had-- I had the sicknesses there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had, like I told you, I didn't eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then when I came out, that's the worst part.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's important.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When I came out, I was feeling great, great.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was-- I worked a year in, in Greece and was-- then I went-- before, when I went to England, everything started coming-- showing the effects of the camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I started to have-- my nerves in my system-- not in my head, in my system were weakened.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I didn't know that nerves had a-- give you a problem.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I thought nerves were when you're mentally sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But when my body started to feel-- I couldn't breathe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In England, I was-- I went to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was looking around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I say-- I couldn't get my breath out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And for a month I was choking-- for a year.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then at last, I decided to go to the doctor next door.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was a Jewish doctor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I went in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was so bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I throw everything I was doing, and I go there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I say-- there were so many people there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She says, who are you? the nurse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I say-- I say, I want to see the doctor right now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She's-- but-- and the doctor heard me crying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, come on in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I say-- and she-- and he saw-- and I saw my number in my arm.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says-- she says, your heart is fine, she says.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
